author: Alec Leach
title: We Shot Gucci’s SS17 Collection in an Old Milan Dancehall
text:
Visit the original post to see all 7 images from this gallery. 
Location: Sala Venezia, Via Alvise Cadamosto, Milan, Italy.
Season: Spring/Summer 2017
Key Looks: Every single getup is a visual buffet, but the heavily-embellished denim pieces are extra-decadent.
Editor’s Notes: This editorial was shot in Milanese dance hall “Sala Venezia”, a suitably lavish location to showcase Gucci’s SS17 collection. The shoot is titled “Gucci Symphony,” inspired by “Ghetto Symphony,” A$AP Rocky’s song feat. A$AP Ferg and Gunplay.
